---
layout: layouts/page.njk
---
<article class="max-w-3xl prose prose-zinc dark:prose-invert mx-auto p-8">

  <!-- Back -->

  <a href="/" class="block">
    <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-orange-600 px-3 py-0.5 text-sm font-medium text-white">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-3 h-3">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 19.5L8.25 12l7.5-7.5" />
      </svg>
      <span>
        &nbsp;All posts
      </span>
    </span>
  </a>

  <!-- Title -->

  <h1 class="mb-0 mt-4">
    {{ title }}
  </h1>

  <!-- Meta -->

  <p class="text-md mt-2">
    <span class="text-zinc-500">
      {{ data.date | publishDate }} in
    </span>
    <span class="text-zinc-500">
      {%- for tag in data.tags or tags -%}
        {%- if tag != "post" -%}
          {{ tag }}
        {%- endif -%}
      {%- endfor -%}
    </span>
    <span class="text-zinc-500">
      Â· {{ content | readingTime }}
    </span>
  </p>

  <!-- Content -->

  <div class="pt-8">
    {{ content | safe }}
  </div>

  <!-- CTA -->

  <div>
    <hr class="h-px my-8 bg-zinc-200 border-0 dark:bg-zinc-700">
    <aside role="note" class="note rounded-md bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800 p-4">
      <div class="flex">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6 text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-50 mt-0.5">
            <path d="M16.881 4.346A23.112 23.112 0 018.25 6H7.5a5.25 5.25 0 00-.88 10.427 21.593 21.593 0 001.378 3.94c.464 1.004 1.674 1.32 2.582.796l.657-.379c.88-.508 1.165-1.592.772-2.468a17.116 17.116 0 01-.628-1.607c1.918.258 3.76.75 5.5 1.446A21.727 21.727 0 0018 11.25c0-2.413-.393-4.735-1.119-6.904zM18.26 3.74a23.22 23.22 0 011.24 7.51 23.22 23.22 0 01-1.24 7.51c-.055.161-.111.322-.17.482a.75.75 0 101.409.516 24.555 24.555 0 001.415-6.43 2.992 2.992 0 00.836-2.078c0-.806-.319-1.54-.836-2.078a24.65 24.65 0 00-1.415-6.43.75.75 0 10-1.409.516c.059.16.116.321.17.483z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="ml-3 flex-1 md:flex md:justify-between">
          <p class="text-md text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-50 m-0 font-medium">
            I hope you enjoyed reading the article and learned something practical. Feel free to share your feedback at any time by <a href="mailto:hi@untypical.dev" class="underline text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-50">sending me an email</a>.
            <br />
            <br />
            I'd appreciate it if you'd share this article with other people who might be interested in it. Thank you!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</article>
